name: Xanadu Mona Lisa
description:
Contemporary sacred art. A transfiguration of my "Buddha Lisa" that takes my technique to the next level (this includes hand drawing and AI enhancements).

Towards the bottom you may notice some writings. It's the first verses of "Kubla Khan" a famous visionary poem by Coleridge ("In Xanadu did Kubla Khan
A stately pleasure-dome decree...)
